<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 06:18:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>焦点：尽管欧盟正在考虑关税，但欧洲国家仍在争夺中国电动汽车工厂和就业机会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-nations-compete-chinese-ev-factories-jobs-even-eu-weighs-tariffs-2024-06-10/</link><description>欧洲各国政府可能对中国廉价电动汽车涌入其市场持谨慎态度，但他们也在激烈竞争新竞争对手带来的制造业投资和就业份额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 06:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-nations-compete-chinese-ev-factories-jobs-even-eu-weighs-tariffs-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>市场：美国如何鼓励世界寻找美元替代品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/market-how-us-is-daring-world-find-dollar-alternative-2024-06-10/</link><description>美国正在兴高采烈地削弱支撑美元作为世界储备货币的支柱，最新的打击来自一些有权势的美国人在唐纳德·特朗普被定罪后对法治提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 05:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/market-how-us-is-daring-world-find-dollar-alternative-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰总理称中国总理李强本周将访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-pm-says-china-premier-li-qiang-visit-this-week-2024-06-10/</link><description>新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周一表示，中国总理李强将于本周访问新西兰，这是中国总理七年来首次访华。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 04:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-zealand-pm-says-china-premier-li-qiang-visit-this-week-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>韩美将在首尔举行新一轮核计划会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-hold-new-round-nuclear-planning-talks-seoul-2024-06-10/</link><description>首尔官员表示，出于对平壤不断增长的核武库的担忧，韩国和美国定于周一在首尔举行会谈，讨论在与朝鲜的战争期间更好地协调盟国的核反应。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 03:10:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-hold-new-round-nuclear-planning-talks-seoul-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下跌，政治不确定性扰乱欧元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-10/</link><description>鉴于美国劳动力市场依然紧张，交易员大幅削减了对美联储今年降息的押注，亚洲股市周一下跌，而法国提前大选的呼声引发了更广泛的政治担忧，并打压欧元。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 02:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>马克龙呼吁法国提前大选 欧元跌至一个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-slips-one-month-low-macron-calls-french-election-2024-06-10/</link><description>法国总统马克龙呼吁提前举行立法选举后，欧元周一大幅下跌，受到政治不确定性的打击，而美元在本周晚些时候的美联储会议之前保持坚挺。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 01:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-slips-one-month-low-macron-calls-french-election-2024-06-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国家居去库存行动并未给开发商带来多少欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-de-stocking-push-bring-developers-little-cheer-2024-06-09/</link><description>分析师和开发商表示，由于该计划规模有限且价格可能较低，中国通过将未售出的房屋转变为经济适用房来清理大量库存的努力不太可能帮助资金紧张的开发商。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 23:09:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-home-de-stocking-push-bring-developers-little-cheer-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：从贸易到气候，欧盟选举的五个要点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/trade-climate-five-takeaways-eu-election-2024-06-09/</link><description>周日结束为期四天的选举后，欧洲议会右倾，欧洲怀疑论民族主义者增多，主流自由派和绿党减少。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 22:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/trade-climate-five-takeaways-eu-election-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着日本央行和美联储的临近，削减风险敞口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-09/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 21:49:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，美国和沙特阿拉伯即将敲定安全条约草案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-saudi-arabia-close-finalizing-draft-security-treaty-wsj-reports-2024-06-09/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》周日援引美国和沙特的消息报道，拜登政府即将与沙特阿拉伯敲定一项条约，该条约将承诺美国帮助保卫这个海湾国家，作为旨在鼓励利雅得与以色列之间外交关系的协议的一部分官员。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-saudi-arabia-close-finalizing-draft-security-treaty-wsj-reports-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲国家世界杯生存之战进入最后阶段</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/battle-world-cup-survival-reaches-endgame-asian-nations-2024-06-09/</link><description>周二，11 个国家将争夺 2026 年世界杯亚洲区预选赛下一阶段剩余的 5 个席位，其中中国、印度和印度尼西亚的命运尚未确定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 17:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/battle-world-cup-survival-reaches-endgame-asian-nations-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国进军南海挑衅军备竞赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-us-provoking-arms-race-moves-into-south-china-sea-2024-06-09/</link><description>中国外交部副部长孙卫东在周日发表的讲话中表示，美国在南海构成了最大的安全挑战，因为其在那里的军事部署正在将南海变成“军备竞赛的漩涡”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 12:31:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-us-provoking-arms-race-moves-into-south-china-sea-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，七国集团计划就与俄罗斯的关系向中资小型银行发出警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-plans-warn-small-chinese-banks-over-russia-ties-sources-say-2024-06-09/</link><description>本周在意大利举行的七国集团峰会的领导人预计将在非公开会议上重点讨论中俄贸易对乌克兰冲突造成的威胁以及应对措施。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 12:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-plans-warn-small-chinese-banks-over-russia-ties-sources-say-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>图普洛图因内侧韧带受伤至少缺席六周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/medial-ligament-injury-sidelines-tuipulotu-least-six-weeks-2024-06-09/</link><description>奥克兰蓝队队长帕特里克·图普洛图在周六战胜斐济德鲁亚队的四分之一决赛中膝盖受伤，将缺席超级太平洋橄榄球赛季的剩余比赛。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 05:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/medial-ligament-injury-sidelines-tuipulotu-least-six-weeks-2024-06-09/</guid></item><item><title>据《泰晤士报》报道，沃尔沃将电动汽车生产转移到比利时以避免中国关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-shifting-ev-production-belgium-evade-china-tariffs-times-reports-2024-06-09/</link><description>据《泰晤士报》周六报道，沃尔沃汽车已开始将中国制造的电动汽车生产转移到比利时，预计欧盟将继续打击北京补贴的进口汽车。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 05:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-shifting-ev-production-belgium-evade-china-tariffs-times-reports-2024-06-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>